From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000028 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: SharpWine Contributors <sharpwine@example.invalid>
Date: Sat, 18 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] gem: execute i386 avx miscellaneous destinations

Implement AVX forms whose destinations are GPRs, flags, MXCSR, scalar
register/memory slots, or implicitly selected vector registers. Reuse reviewed
legacy semantics only after exact VEX admission, and add native movemask,
move, insert, and extract handlers with exact width and upper-lane behavior.

---
diff -ruN --exclude=*.orig a/blink/avx.c b/blink/avx.c
--- a/blink/avx.c	2026-07-18 01:43:47
+++ b/blink/avx.c	2026-07-18 01:44:57
@@ -57,12 +57,12 @@
